<topic id="adding_inline_actions">
    <title>Adding Inline Actions</title>
    <body>
        <p>Using the <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/button-editor.html"
                format="html" scope="external">oxy_button</xref> and <xref
                href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/button-group-editor.html"
                format="html" scope="external">oxy_buttonGroup</xref> form controls you can add
            inline actions in the Author visual editing mode. As an example, you can open a
            LightWeight DITA topic from the folder <b>OXYGEN_INSTALL_DIR\samples\dita\lw-dita/</b>. </p>
    </body>
</topic>
